":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19013,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/07\/seek-refuge-seven-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":34710,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Death: Seek refuge in Allah from seven deaths","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 7, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSeek refuge in Allah from seven kinds of death: a sudden death, a snake bite, a predator, a fire, drowning, something falling above or below, and being killed whilst fleeing a marching army.\u201d Source: Musnad\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1060,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/10\/22\/seek-refuge-disability-laziness\/","url_meta":{"origin":34710,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Grant my soul righteousness and purify it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Arqam reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would supplicate, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from disability, sloth, cowardice, miserliness, senility, and the punishment of the grave. O Allah, grant my soul a sense of righteousness and purify it, for You are\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33028,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/seek-refuge-entering-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":34710,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seek refuge from Satan when entering mosque","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered the mosque, he would say, \u201cI seek refuge in Allah Almighty, in his noble countenance, and in his everlasting authority from the accursed Satan.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 466 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34710","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=34710"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34710\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=34710"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy